{
  "stem": "21786.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "The rest you know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I didn't get so far.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh yes, yes, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] One of them was my friend whose name was the Reichmann, R-E-I-C-H-M-A-N-N.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The first name was Richard.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I could give you some names, but they wouldn't probably mean too much.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I really do.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were even permitted to be trained, you know, by the SS, permitted us to be trained in British [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] army commands.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Like, we had to know, we have to-- we had to be aware that you have to probably jump overboard, swim to the sea-- seashore, that there were people from the kibbutz.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we'll mix into it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then we come to the coast, so we will be arrested by the British.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we will be interrogated now.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We had to know Hebrew.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We had to know some kind of English.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we had to know the British commands.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they let us have some kind of wooden sticks by which we trained on all kinds of the [INAUDIBLE] and similar, the Hebrew commands or the British commands which were quite different from the commands in the Czech army or the Czech boy scouts or-- or the Y-camp or whatever-- where ever I came before.",
      "word_count": 56
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Anyhow, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] return to the Department of the Solution of the Jewish Question.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Interestingly enough, they knew plenty of the Zionist leaders, these SS Men.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "For the Zionists, they have the same goal as the Germans wanted them to have.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And that is to get the Jews out of Europe.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "In the '30s, simply it was done simply by release, by paying certain amount of money and, later on, simply by seizure of all the property and everything.",
      "word_count": 28
    }
  ],
